originalText.text: Tatjana has helped me learn about my health and well-being while providing me with acupuncture treatments over the last year. She is wonderful and very professional. She has great suggestions and works with the whole person rather than just your symptoms. Highly recommended!!

originalText.text: I have been working with Tatjana for many months now and she has helped with various injuries, old and new. Acupuncture was the missing piece in a series of treatments I'd tried to relieve chronic back and side pain. Tatjana is the kindest, most thoughtful practitioner and she has a wealth of knowledge.

originalText.text: Tatjana is a thorough, thoughtful practitioner with experience in a wide range of treatments (acupuncture, gua sha, cupping, Chinese herbs and supplements) - I have seen her for everything from chronic anxiety and tension to sports injuries to allergies to insomnia to digestive issues. Tatjana has a lovely peaceful demeanor; I respect her and have had great success working with her on my holistic health. She’s extremely responsive by email, and her practice offers electronic booking via Genbook (which is very easy to use and convenient).

originalText.text: Tatjana is an amazing acupuncturist. I went to a hoakey one a year ago and it was terrible. Tatjana will ask you so many questions about what’s ailing you and come up with a whole plan and tell you what she’s going to do. I felt so much better meeting a real acupuncturist
